data.description: WOW! This Grand Home has an Assumable VA Loan at **2.75%** interest rate, to Qualified Buyers.  For Details please text or email Rich Plasmeier the Listing Agent.  A Stately Brick Front Ext: features the Grandeur of Soaring 2 story High Ceilings 18' in Foyer & Great Room. Elegant Great Room with Timeless Mantel Fireplace &  Upscale Built-in Cabinetry w Design & TV.  Home features flooring of Stylish Grey tones Wood like planks that are tile throughout Main Floors adding to Stylish Decor.  The Spacious Kitchen is a Chef’s dream: Rich Cherry Cabinets, Gorgeous Slab Granite Ctops, ST ST Appl, & Walk-in Pantry.  Spacious Main Floor Primary Bedroom has High Vaulted Ceilings featuring Double Door Entry & Double Barn Doors to Bath.  Primary Bath has Radiant Heated Flooring, Spacious Unique Walk-in Shower having RAIN Head shower & Hand Wand Fixtures.  Beautiful Bath Vanity Upgraded with Stylish Quartz Ctop & other Design Elements.   Main Floor Front Office: Grand Design with Bay Windows, Vaulted Ceilings, & French Doors.  Formal Dining Room/ 2nd Office w Entry to Kitchen.  Newer Large Deck with maintenance Free Flooring, Railing, Solar Lights, & Below a Cement Patio.  Interior 2nd Floor Open Stairway entry to 3 Adult sized Bedrooms having Walk-In-Closets, Bonus Room, Updated Fixtures & Finishes to 2nd Floor Full Bath with Radiant Heated Flooring.  Spacious Finished Walk-out Basement: Carpeted Large Family/Game Room, Double Doors to Gym, & Private Bedroom with Ensuite 3/4 Bath. This Unique Luxurious Home featuring Upgrades & High Design Style items throughout.  Pride of Ownership has been added throughout Home Many Grand Stylish Upgrades.  Anthology Community has Swimming Pools, Parks w Playgrounds, Trails, & Grand Modern Clubhouse.   The location of home is walkable to Elementary School & Close to Restaurants, Shopping, & Activities. This is a Luxury Home in a Prime Community with Updates & Finishes throughout.  This Dream Home a Great Opportunity with Low Maintenance.
